data.description: BEAUTIFUL , SPACIOUS, COMPLETELY RENOVATED 2 BEDROOM 1 BATH CORNER UNIT CONDO WITH LAKE VIEW !!! This amazing condo is completely turnkey ready ! Renovated home in the wonderful community of Carrington! This home features an open layout, newer flooring, updated appliances, AC , updated and remodeled kitchen, large spacious bedrooms, dual marble sink vanity, and much much more!  Resort style living!! This wonderful community features a gated security entrance, a beautiful clubhouse with an amazing pool, jacuzzi, gym, playroom, indoor racquet ball court, business center and more. Valet Trash!!  Amazing school zone and conveniently located next to great shopping centers and restaurants.  Don't miss out on this amazing home and come see this property today!!! Available for immediate move in!
